{"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/rosrealitydemo\/rosrealityhelper"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Apple’s visionOS natively supports USD and also uses reality(Apple’s 3D Model representation format) but there is no native solution that can convert URDFs to reality or USD. There is a tool from NVIDIA that does convert URDF to USD but it not yet tested on Apple Platforms like macOS or visionOS.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"As a part of the thesis, RosRealityHelper - a macOS application was developed that can convert ROS2 robot description packages to reality was created. This application currently takes a ROS Robot description package along with the URDF file as inputs and converts it to the reality file which can be viewed any Apple devices. Current implementation of the praser works on Manipulators. This uses the Scenekit API to convert the STL and DAE files to the reality file format with additional metadata to make it interactable using the Direct and Indirect gestures of visionOS."}]}],"kind":"content"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo\/RosRealityHelper"},"metadata":{"title":"RosRealityHelper","modules":[{"name":"Master Thesis Showcase"}],"roleHeading":"Article","role":"article"},"kind":"article","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"ROS Robot Description Converter","type":"text"}],"sampleCodeDownload":{"action":{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/igm-git.igm.rwth-aachen.de\/projekte\/apple-space\/applications\/rosrealityhelper","overridingTitle":"Visit"},"kind":"sampleDownload"},"seeAlsoSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo\/RclSwift","doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo\/RosRealityViewTemplate","doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo\/RosRealityViewer"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"sections":[],"references":{"doc://RosRealityDemo/documentation/RosRealityDemo/RosRealityViewer":{"role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/rosrealitydemo\/rosrealityviewer","identifier":"doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo\/RosRealityViewer","type":"topic","title":"RosRealityViewer","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Apple Vision Pro Application, which can interact with the ROS network and display interactable ROS Entities and Visualization."}],"kind":"article"},"doc://RosRealityDemo/documentation/RosRealityDemo/RosRealityViewTemplate":{"role":"article","url":"\/documentation\/rosrealitydemo\/rosrealityviewtemplate","identifier":"doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo\/RosRealityViewTemplate","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"A 3D Asset catalog for ROS programms","type":"text"}],"title":"RosRealityViewTemplate","kind":"article"},"https://igm-git.igm.rwth-aachen.de/projekte/apple-space/applications/rosrealityhelper":{"checksum":null,"identifier":"https:\/\/igm-git.igm.rwth-aachen.de\/projekte\/apple-space\/applications\/rosrealityhelper","url":"https:\/\/igm-git.igm.rwth-aachen.de\/projekte\/apple-space\/applications\/rosrealityhelper","type":"download"},"doc://RosRealityDemo/documentation/RosRealityDemo":{"role":"collection","identifier":"doc:\/\/RosRealityDemo\/documentation\/RosRealityDemo","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/rosrealitydemo","abstract":[{"text":"This pages documents certain insights gained while working on my master thesis - A modular framework for building AR Applications on Apple XR Devices interacting with ROS-based Robots.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"Master Thesis Showcase"},"doc://RosRealityDemo/documentation/RosRealityDemo/RclSwift":{"kind":"article","url":"\/documentation\/rosreali